  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Transaction Release: Work Item List</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio25d6c7533a661d4be10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Transaction Release: Work Item List</h1><div class=\"body\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Use</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> Here, you can display a list of the transactions that still need to be processed.\n</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Information System</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction </span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Transaction Release </span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Transaction Release: Work Items, Money Market.</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction Release: Work Item Overview and Status of all Transactions</span> screen appears <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">.</span> Enter the selection criteria in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction data</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Additional data</span> areas.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Program</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">. The workflow data is read.</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">An overview of the status of the transactions selected is displayed. The status of a work item shows you the status of this step within the workflow.\n</p></li></ol>\n<p class=\"p\"><img class=\"inline\" src=\"loio454470533fe4761ee10000000a174cb4_LowRes.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"> You can also release transactions using the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Release workflow.</span>\n</p>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
